data.description: Located in the Arrowhead S/D, near DeRidder Schools and West Park.  This home features 3 bedrooms (new carpet in owners bedroom) and 2 full baths, Living room that is accented with vaulted ceiling and a wood burning fireplace, separate formal dining area, an interior storage room, 2 car garage and large fenced back yard. You're sure to enjoy the large covered, screened in back patio. Perfect for morning coffee or evening cookouts. New, complete HVAC system, new water heater, new dishwasher.Schedule your viewing!
